<p><img src=http://www.ocediscovery.com/images/global-template/discovery-2013-ontario-centres-of-excellence.png?sfvrsn=6 class=blogpic></p>

<p>Completely off the Robocar track is a short <a href="http://www.cnbc.com/id/101770345">interview with CNBC</a> where I advise people to invest in Bitcoin related technology, not in bitcoins.</p>
